condition.narrative: The Recipient shall not later than three (3) months from the Effective Date, establish and maintain within its Ministry of Finance,a Project Coordination Unit (PCU) responsible for the day-to-day implementation and coordination of the Project. See SectionI.A.1(a) of Schedule 2 of Financing Agreement.

The Recipient shall, not later than four (4) months from the Effective Date, prepare and furnish to the Association, an Accountingand Procedures Manual satisfactory to the Association. See Section IV.1 of Schedule 2 of Financing Agreement.
